      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2021 R2 is a commercially validated FEA solver with documented V&V procedures. FDA in-house scripts underwent peer review and regression testing. Version control via Git with tagged release. SQA documentation meets Gradation 3 requirements per ASME V&V 40 Table 3."
    },
    {
