      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2.",
      "rationale": "Benchmark patch tests and single-element verification cases confirm correct implementation of linear hexahedral and tetrahedral element formulations. Manufacturer-supplied verification manual covers contact mechanics and large-deformation regimes relevant to this COU."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
